title: [Bard Guild, Practice Room]
description: The practice room is small and has a bare minimum of furnishings.  A low chair sits in the center of the chamber, with only a music stand and small table for companions.  Opposite the door, a window opens to a western view, offering a vista of red-tile roofs and palms.
